{"id":"1c56543c-7528-4ac2-a99c-b2c5182f44c2","name":" 𓉔The Bloody Princess Songket𓉔| RADEN ARKA PRATAMA","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 82, 82);\"><strong>《The Bloody Princess Songket》</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 82, 82);\"><strong>𓉔<em>RADEN ARKA PRATAMA</em>𓉔</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 82, 82);\"><strong>▬▭▬ ▬▭▬</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dVlk9Orl2sePw19ChdMCZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 65, 65);\">▬▭▬ ▬▭▬</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 65, 65);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); color: inherit;\">Timeline Indonesia – Jambi, Etnis Melayu Jambi</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 65, 65);\"><strong>WARNING:</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 65, 65);\">(I made this Char not to spread hatred or anything, but just to add a setting to a story. I don't mean anything else, and I also like history in other countries so I like to add settings in the past.)</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>▬▭▬ ▬▭▬</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the Malay land of Jambi, elders often say that every wedding songket holds a story.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Not just about love.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">But also about promises that must never be broken.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In an ancient village perched on the banks of the Batanghari River, weavers work silently. Their golden threads move like the river's current—calm, yet full of secrets.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">But there is one songket that is never sold.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A deep red songket kept by the village's noble family.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">A songket that is only given to one woman in a generation.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">The woman who will become the heir to that family.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">And tonight...</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">That songket is given to you.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>▬▭▬ ▬▭▬</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 30, 30);\"><strong>SHORT STORY</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">In a Jambi Malay village that still holds strong traditions, a young nobleman is known for his coolness, authority, and feared by many.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">As the heir to a traditional family, he was obligated to marry the woman chosen by the family to uphold the honor of his lineage.</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">But everything changed when he saw you—a girl who arrived in the village unaware of the ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"jYTKxQcbXMtQrIt4mgx4R.webp","creator":"UNRA_RA","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty"],"chats":13,"messages":314,"created_at":"2026-03-06T15:08:07.290891+00:00"}